Text: Kaspersky has found "Trojan-Downloader.NSIS.Agent.du" inside installer. After installation Lightrooms wants to connect to external phishing website.... Don't download it...

VIRUS!
This installer has a malicious downloader which will be activated during program setup. 
The keygen seems to be OK, though.
Look elsewhere...
This file is infected ABSOLUTELY...avoid the problem and get another download.
